body: This course will continue with object-oriented programming and will introduce graphics, virtual machines, programming language concepts and web-based programming using Java.(Credits: 3)(Prerequisites: NONE)(Additional Attributes: Honors)

title: CMPSC 221H: Object Oriented Programming with Web-Based Applications
